50|$|The {{first season}} follows Carrie Mathison, a Central Intelligence Agency {{operations}} officer who, after conducting an unauthorized <b>operation</b> <b>in</b> <b>Iraq,</b> {{is put on}} probation and reassigned to the CIA's Counterterrorism Center in Langley, Virginia. <b>In</b> <b>Iraq,</b> Carrie was warned by an asset that an American prisoner of war had been turned by al-Qaeda. Carrie has also been diagnosed with bipolar disorder, a fact that she conceals from the CIA. She surreptitiously receives medication for the disorder from her sister.|$|R
